column4: Text
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "06D383DA4D7ADDC66961E39F75380BC6", "Join the official Torchlight Frontiers Discord server via http://discord.gg/playtorchlight")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "D2DF89154F95903C56E321A4CE2135E2", "Press Tab on the keyboard to toggle between the minimap and an overlay map of the area.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "862BCAD84888B3E0D1DEDF9218A04640", "Press M or Left Arrow on the D-Pad to toggle the frontier map and quest log.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "0DC0E2B74EF264C044E028A407FD24E4", "Hold Shift to attack in place.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "BFBDE55E4D32BEDEA4F2158269F5B7AA", "Press Z to open a travel portal. This can be used anywhere except in boss arenas, towns, and forts.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "F422EDCE46448A8D2FE12980B1342607", "Press Q to use a potion.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "DF24CDD040D02E96EEAF6BAFB6851950", "Press I to open your inventory.")
NSLOCTEXT("[EF45CE9A42E1C2109AAA4DA845845F2D]", "1FC8AFED4020F961B520F0BFA3881996", "Press R to open the skills menu.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "5BC455114D66F879DB5D869D2127A642", "Press C to open the contracts menu.")
NSLOCTEXT("[EF45CE9A42E1C2109AAA4DA845845F2D]", "EB6CC74F45EAA530326E74833EDACF09", "Press E to swap to your equipped Relic.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "915263DF4924B14F26C966932FB417FE", "Press V to quickly zoom in on your character. Use Mouse Wheel Up or Mouse Wheel Down to zoom in or out.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "C860D2B545A3F0047577F0B9D607B249", "Press F12 to hide/unhide the interface.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "4D1EC4CA49512A74393EB486D67294DE", "Press \\ (backslash) to toggle the quest tracker.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "01D4FB7649E26236663C19A1F586F843", "Press ESC to open the options menu or close a UI window.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "D80CC93F4F007C543A118BA5F3B21493", "Press ENTER or / (forward slash) to chat in game.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "60D4BE3D4E2EF912E43441B73AD2AF62", "Press H to toggle the help menu.")
NSLOCTEXT("[EF45CE9A42E1C2109AAA4DA845845F2D]", "0C1BDDD542AA1338ED1F76967A61F77F", "Press F or Up on the D-Pad while in your fort to customize your fort.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "DF08161C4CFBEC7172074C84D0E2EE9A", "Use the Send Pet to Town button in the Pet Inventory to send your pet to town to sell items.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "7799C8E74621756E40B274B4EBE852B6", "Press X with an item selected from your inventory to move an item to your pet\'s inventory tab.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "246122C84E528A758BD753A0A80FB728", "Press P to open the party menu.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "AC5FFAC549975DA5D30221941DADEC01", "Press C while in the inventory menu to toggle your stats.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "5D7DF391403233429912D1B474783AA5", "Hold D to destroy an item from your inventory. This action cannot be undone!")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "ED9D415345E220925E1DD4B384C58F18", "Travel quickly between unlocked waypoints found throughout the world.")
NSLOCTEXT("[EF45CE9A42E1C2109AAA4DA845845F2D]", "8EA7131E48DDFC96ADEDE086A1210C85", "Fame can be earned from completing quests, killing champions and bosses.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "4B4B25A04507094EB783FCA8F8BF4A85", "Build a Reliquary in your fort to craft and store your Relics.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "6D89F32544CD97EC205CD3A6EFAE5EC7", "Relics become more powerful per level.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "0AA071F841C58F48CE1DB1B68A373714", "Unique Relic powers can be unlocked as your experience with a Relic increases.")
NSLOCTEXT("[EF45CE9A42E1C2109AAA4DA845845F2D]", "37E7DB7F4752C4906E8B2C838767A4C3", "Build a Sawmill in your fort to craft Wood Planks from Wood Logs you\'ve gathered.")
NSLOCTEXT("[EF45CE9A42E1C2109AAA4DA845845F2D]", "4B0879B742DDF1FA21A7B58D7BD0F56D", "Build a Smelter in your fort to craft Metal Bars from Metal Nuggets you\'ve gathered.")
NSLOCTEXT("[EF45CE9A42E1C2109AAA4DA845845F2D]", "3AAC4D5A44E168F1C3275980C5DDAED6", "Build a Stonemason in your fort to craft Stone Blocks from Stone Rocks you\'ve gathered.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "B6ABC17644BED970A194D18663FE9AD3", "Other players can randomly encounter your fort in public passages. Customize your fort by building and placing decorations.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "10724B7746666B6C4347A1A0FB1CDF1B", "Lifebound items have slightly better affixes but are immediately destroyed if the character dies. ")

NSLOCTEXT("[EF45CE9A42E1C2109AAA4DA845845F2D]", "C074F1B04547B710700A4E9FABB3C0E2", "Boss Chests may drop a Scroll of Unbinding. Use this on a Lifebound item to remove its bind to your lifeforce, allowing you to keep the powerful item, even if you die.")

NSLOCTEXT("[EF45CE9A42E1C2109AAA4DA845845F2D]", "479616B8472BE88E5B04278641156162", "Gain Respectacles by leveling up, defeating bosses or gaining contract levels. These allow you to refund a skill point at a skill station in a fort.")

NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "716B4990408B29AB08B9E58CC0EC2FDA", "Relics, forged by the fallen Dwarven empire, are considerably more powerful than standard weapons. Due to their magical and semi-corporeal composition, they can only be used for brief moments at a time.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "C8A37E6A41D216E9EE58408EE44AC244", "The Netherim lurk in a realm beyond, always seeking to tear their way into the world at its most vulnerable points.")

NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "DC6A8B5D443372DACA525399D6012DAF", "The Netherim have infiltrated civilizations and ranks of power inside Nether-hosts to manipulate and build an ember-blighted uprising.")

NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "DED8097045DC0B8DFD8F56964F9BF5C1", "Humans and goblins have a long history of hatred and distrust. The shores on both the human and goblin side bear the marks of past battles and skirmishes.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "34ED1B354382139A0114288C245FCAC8", "The Hyvid Citadel is the heart of the Hyvid colony, a bustling cave that houses the Hyvid Queen.")

NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "Lore_Hyvid_001_Text", "The Hyvid often come into conflict with the goblins, who have taken to building a firewall across the border between the goblin forest and the infested forest.")

NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "Lore_Hyvid_002_Text", "The \"Charger Bug\" is not a member of the Hyvid species, but is a symbiotic species that uses its destructive strength to smash through the environment, providing places for Hyvid to build.")

NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "Lore_Hyvid_003_Text", "The Hyvid in the infested forest originally arrived on Zul’Rasha over 100 years ago, adrift on a barge-like chunk of a larger hive that broke off of a nearby Hyvid island colony.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "Lore_Hyvid_004_Text", "When a Hyvid colony has exceeded its land mass, a portion of the hive mass is made to break away and float on the seas to form a new colony.")

NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "3522A29043DE89013FEE498927476160", "Initially an eschatological cult, the Order of Dusk arose in response to the strange behavior of ember around the Torchlight site.")

NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "C39DE016454E76D6E68348BC856A6898", "Dusk Mages rely on Mana, using Dark and Light skills to build up energy. When one type of energy is full, use a skill of the opposite type to trigger a buff.")

NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "6BC58F28405C55F2C640BF8A5EB935C0", "The Railmasters are the clever, technically-minded men and women of the Rail Kingdoms who learned to use the ancient Dwarven technologies for building rails and trains.")

NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "FF37AFC74E0A5749B1A270BE0DB30654", "Railmasters use Endurance for most skills. They can also place tracks to allow their train\'s abilities to support them in combat.")

NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "54C3A9E34DED1D4C3BFE498FEFE2D1C1", "The Forged remained directionless in the cold and dark for hundreds of years until a group of human explorers stumbled into the ruins of Herzgart.")

NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "57C01A044DE2F4C5EF3372B2E1A92C83", "The Forged builds up Heat and consumes Heat to use Vent skills. Venting at higher heat levels increases the effectiveness of the skill. ")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "7667EB7A4D5F6928ED2A01B9FA63A9E3", "The tales of a massive, terrible Goblin were no myth. Wideload is the scourge of the Goblin battlefields.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "4A974A31436F2D8F72294998AA6B98B5", "For years, Wideload has terrorized Imperial Soldiers. On the battlefield, he is unstoppable.")
column17: Warp from Gob forest 1 - Gob forest 2

column4: NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "5192647941CCB876FE93B7AE7E7F3BC9", "Wideload doesn’t usually start battles, he ends them. The only hope we have is to get him where he lives.")
column17: Warp from Gob Forest 2 - Gob Forest 3

column4: NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "92807BF3492F1CAB81145B833F392905", "Wideload\'s Lair is rumored to lie deep within the caves of the Goblin Stash.")
column17: Warp from Gob Forest 3 - Wideload’s Cave

column4: NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "49F69A5A477655731BF517A05AA6E751", "Whoever vanquishes Wideload will earn the trust of all Imperial Soldiers. The reward for his death will be Wideload’s Ceremonial Shield, a trophy worthy of a hero.")
column17: Warp from Wideload’s Cave - Wideload’s Lair

column4: NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "0B48D9C54887109D257448AA806746B7", "Recent seismic activity revealed evidence of deep, hollow caverns. Some say that a distinct \"krronk!\" continues to echo throughout the caverns.")
NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "FB297B98484784031698CAA57B2802F2", "The Hyvid obeys Krru\'sha, their Hyvid queen above all else.")

NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "C28CD4BA43B9EDFA717F22BCF43FE46A", "Although the Hyvid queen controls the Hive, otherworldly forces have taken ahold of its ruler, and a new usurper queen has taken its place.")

NSLOCTEXT("LoadingScreenTable", "DDFD6EE642C6D9BD3F3D6388BEE6827B", "Sadista has taken control of the Hyvid Capital, using the Hyvid queen as her puppet. Drive her out before the Hyvid overwhelms us all.")
